item.description: Hello # This UI kit has is to assist with Web based projects that rely on common frontend frameworks. As it develops, it will provide css files that will serve RMIT User Interface elements and compile theme here. Compiled css file As each element is mapped and coded to a Bootstrap element, it will appear in the ‘compenents’ menu on the left of this screen. At this time limited components are available.

item.title: Help
item.description: Hi there. # This is a rainy day weather project for the rapid building of RMIT UI interfaces. It’s not endorsed by central marketing or CX teams, though aims to provide a playbook for the dozens of digital environments that are expected to conform to RMIT brand guidelines. For more info, please contact the RMIT University Libray Digital Learning Team
